                    Test 22 History file
                    --------------------
This file should be used by the test developer to briefly
summarize all major modifications introduced in the code and keep
track of all tags.

     ----------------------------------------------------------
     * Reverse chronological order (last date on top), please *
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

20 February 2015 Gunter Folger                    (test22-V10-00-02)
- CMakeLists.txt: add missing DEPEND on build step 

19  February 2015 Gunter Folger
---------------------------------------------------------------------
- Revising CMakeLists.txt to eliminate configure warnings: only 
     test22_NA49 is used for testing, others may be build like examples.

11 February 2015 Andrea Dotti
---------------------------------------------------------------------
- Adding OPTIONAL to the install cmake command to avoid problems
  when issuing make install and testing is enabled

25 November 2014 Gunter Folger                     (test22-V10-00-01)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
CMakeLists.txt: set policy CMP0042 to OLD, avoid warning on Mac with recent
CMake concerning new @rpath default.

11 October 2014 Makoto Asai                        (test22-V10-00-00)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
FTFtest1.icc and FTFtest4.icc - replace obsolete G4ParticleTable::GetIon()
to G4IonTable::GetIon().

26 July 2013 Alberto Ribon                         (test22-V09-06-17)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Trying to fix a problem in Windows by using EXCLUDE_FROM_ALL in the
CMakeLists.txt file, as suggested by Ben.

26 July 2013 Alberto Ribon                         (test22-V09-06-16)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Following a new suggestion by Ben, all the CMake build commands are
now condensed into one single, main CMakeLists.txt, whereas the
CMakeLists.txt files in the subdirectories are deleted.

24/25 July 2013 Alberto Ribon/P Gumplinger  (test22-V09-06-14 / - 15)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Changed all CMakeLists.txt (following Ben's suggestion) to factorize
into a common library the shared code between all tests; retagged as
test22-V09-06-15.

